title: Green Salmon Coffee and Tea House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee shop and cafe offering vegetarian and a couple vegan choices. Focus is on fairly-traded and organic ingredients. Features organic coffee, loose leaf tea, and a small menu of from-scratch baked sweets and savories.
